Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.71,0:02:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.05,0:02:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World, the \Nsecond half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.48,0:03:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body \Nturned to rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.32,0:03:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After landing on Punk Hazard; an island with \Ntwo parts, one burning, the other frozen,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.47,0:03:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Straw Hats learned about \Nthe hideous experiments
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.75,0:03:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,performed by Caesar Clown, the Master,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.34,0:03:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and headed off to investigate \Nbut as things got going,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.89,0:03:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy was unexpectedly \Napproached by Trafalgar Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.27,0:03:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna form an alliance \Nwith the Heart Pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.03,0:03:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what we're gonna do is \Nkidnap the Master, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.54,0:03:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the last chance \Nfor you to reconsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.09,0:03:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay. We're with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.55,0:03:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How does it feel to be loose after so long,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.47,0:03:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smiley?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.98,0:04:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Capture M! \NThe Pirate Alliance's Operation Launches!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.72,0:04:10.68,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,THE MOUNTAIN BEHIND THE LABORATORY \NPRESENT
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.99,0:04:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe from when I fell? \NLooks like I hit my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.62,0:04:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, maybe I did, too. I have a huge headache!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.59,0:04:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've wasted so much time. \NI wonder if the samurai is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.55,0:04:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You made us take this side trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.09,0:04:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we all wanted to do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.89,0:04:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a shame that we couldn't find the Yeti.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.60,0:04:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll never forget \Nthe shadows that we saw!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.15,0:04:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't it. Don't fool yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said it was an enemy attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.07,0:04:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.61,0:04:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.99,0:04:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.82,0:04:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.45,0:04:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.12,0:04:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to talk about whether \Nit exists or not forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.21,0:05:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed a little. \NYou're kind of mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.75,0:05:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very old, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.51,0:05:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like that indecisive attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.47,0:05:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Samurai-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.27,0:05:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only we could find traces \Nof his wooden clogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.15,0:05:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.69,0:05:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My breasts are heavy when I run!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.69,0:05:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you wanted to save that samurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.62,0:05:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How romantic!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.58,0:05:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.24,0:05:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if you fall down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.46,0:05:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you two! Take a look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.37,0:05:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a footprint!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.72,0:05:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A trace of his wooden clogs?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.22,0:05:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.76,0:05:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, it must be some centaur's footprint.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:05:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:05:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.50,0:06:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this! Doesn't this look like \Nthe legendary Yeti's footprint?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.62,0:06:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey hey, don't be ridiculous.\N--Hey hey, don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.29,0:06:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, is this for real?! There are \Nmysterious footprints in the snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.79,0:06:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're huge, aren't they?! \NI can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.34,0:06:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they look fresh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.14,0:06:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we follow them, we will find...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,â€¦one of nature's greatest mysteries!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.89,0:06:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dead end?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.09,0:07:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Look! There are huge shadows behind us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me they're the Yeti...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this gas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.05,0:07:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of a zudden, I can't zpeak clearly \Naz if I kot drunk. I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.91,0:07:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iz it an enemy attack?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.53,0:07:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These KYP gas canisters
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.26,0:07:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,make you drunk and drowsy regardless of \Nwhether or not you're a heavy drinker.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.08,0:07:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Down below the cliff is district F-16 \Nfilled with terrible Ice Spikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.16,0:07:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three, for a starter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.06,0:07:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spikes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.11,0:07:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.58,0:08:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.07,0:08:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We left their bodies at the bottom \Nof the cliff in district F-16.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.81,0:08:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you recover them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.50,0:09:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We arrived at district F-16.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.30,0:09:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We found three of the Straw Hats as \Ninformed. We'll recover their dead bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling dead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.02,0:09:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! She's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.23,0:09:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's just a girl - she can't fight us...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter if \Nthere're hundreds of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.94,0:09:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You underlings!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san's body is delicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.00,0:09:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should avoid getting even a single bruise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.33,0:09:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me for having one, Nami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:09:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up, you idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.24,0:10:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, hunting for \Nnature's mysteries is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.26,0:10:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should the samurai be around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think so. He's probably still looking \Nfor his torso around the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.17,0:10:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We almost made it to the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.01,0:10:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Samurai-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, samurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.05,0:10:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Samurai, come on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.22,0:10:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Samurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.56,0:10:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get your ass kicked already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.94,0:10:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on out! Are you alright?! Samurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.16,0:10:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Samurai-san! We're calling you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.99,0:10:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how far he went.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.74,0:10:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he found his torso already \Nand went looking for his son.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.78,0:10:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?! He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.16,0:10:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it! He's frozen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.14,0:11:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1, 2, 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.56,0:11:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey hey, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.54,0:11:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did someone kick your ass?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.11,0:11:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was mysteriously paralyzed \Nand thought I was gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.03,0:11:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just got caught in a snowstorm \Nand froze solid, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.54,0:11:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I don't feel cold at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.24,0:11:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so stubborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.98,0:11:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Warriors don't feel cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's such a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.59,0:11:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get yourself some clothes! \NYou have an ability to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.44,0:11:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-To tell you the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.46,0:12:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because of that magic, I have a weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I became not capable of swimming...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.78,0:12:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't swim, right?! We know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.34,0:12:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What I'm trying to say is my torso is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.32,0:12:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...p-probably soaking in the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.74,0:12:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The water?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.78,0:12:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-In fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.01,0:12:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it feels like the upper half \Nof my body is in the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.52,0:12:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That's why you couldn't even \Nmove and you were frozen here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.19,0:12:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your body's in the water, \Nyou can't use the power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of water, Brook, his torso \Nmay have fallen into the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe. I heard that lake is \Nactually filled with seawater.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.65,0:12:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's still alive here so I don't think \Nit has become food for sharks yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.21,0:12:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we don't know what's in that lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.44,0:12:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We better pull it out as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.42,0:12:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we have to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.71,0:13:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I have to ask you to... um, \Ngo under the water for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.59,0:13:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We know! You can't swim, \Nright? What a crappy samurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.35,0:13:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you people were pirates! \NAnd I'm a total stranger to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.09,0:13:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you helping me so much?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.72,0:13:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm responsible for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.11,0:13:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when you get your whole body back,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.08,0:13:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you have to fight me! I'll kick your ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.60,0:13:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.87,0:13:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I accept it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.26,0:13:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.14,0:13:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh great! Now you're able to say thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.24,0:13:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe getting frozen makes people nicer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.97,0:14:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.53,0:14:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.99,0:14:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Those are...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.23,0:14:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Brownbeard-san's subordino-centaurs \Nthat we robbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Stay with me! Keep running!\N--Get away from the lake!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.53,0:14:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A monster appeared on the other side!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to tell the Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.77,0:14:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where has it been hiding \Non the island until now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.63,0:14:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just keep running! It's gonna come after us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, a monster? You guys are monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.65,0:14:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the pirates who robbed us earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.30,0:14:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! That's my coat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.80,0:14:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about them! Just run! To the lab!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.79,0:14:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They got our Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.42,0:14:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll pay for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.09,0:14:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.80,0:14:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.00,0:14:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Brook. They were coming from the \Nlake that we saw earlier, weren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.30,0:15:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Yes! You got it right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.59,0:15:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed, Zoro-san! And what about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.51,0:15:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if in fact that is the lake,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.12,0:15:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think there was a mountain \Nthere before, was there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.33,0:15:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A mountain?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.02,0:15:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.52,0:16:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smiley is the embodiment of a \Nchemical weapon explosion...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.38,0:16:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that occurred on Punk \NHazard, four years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.57,0:16:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I invented the H2S poison gas bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.36,0:16:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It worked so well
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.11,0:16:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and killed everything on the \Nisland in a matter of seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.81,0:17:26.27,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE YEAR LATER
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.21,0:17:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do they believe I purified \Nthe gas all over the island?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.59,0:17:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! No one would do \Nsuch a wasteful thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.18,0:17:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I compressed it and turned it into a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.43,0:17:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.27,0:17:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smiley!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.60,0:17:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This island was once covered with \Ndead soil where no one could live.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.84,0:18:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People tend to forget tragedies in no time
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.09,0:18:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but that one has lingered here all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.92,0:18:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was always in my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.86,0:18:18.40,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,VEGAPUNK'S FORMER THIRD LABORATORY
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.91,0:18:28.00,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,THE REMAINS OF VEGAPUNK'S \NFORMER FIRST AND SECOND LABORATORY
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never let him take these children again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.13,0:18:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe he was using them as \Nhis test subjects and drugged them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.48,0:18:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't forgive the Master guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.64,0:18:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then let's just go \Nand kidnap the Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.75,0:18:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, if we're too late, \Nwe can't work with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.82,0:18:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not gonna be late. I have an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.84,0:19:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a very good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.10,0:19:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got their ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.66,0:19:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up! Let's finish them off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.51,0:19:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Smoker-san, how can I turn back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.06,0:19:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in my way! Stay still, Tashigi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.98,0:19:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The door is not open yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.53,0:19:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy is in the lab!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.72,0:19:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't just stay out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.46,0:19:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good! The door is as \Nsteady as a rock, Smo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.41,0:19:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel miserable!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.09,0:19:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were in my body, I could easily \Nforce myself into the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.49,0:20:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.22,0:20:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your power is very useful! \NWas it teleportation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.75,0:20:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up and stay inside the bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.10,0:20:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've almost reached the backdoor of the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.66,0:20:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Caesar will probably be in the \Nmain room with that woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.57,0:20:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try to draw them out of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.67,0:20:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to find out about \Nthe drug while we're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.00,0:20:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you can reach the Master that easily
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.39,0:20:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you're so strong, why don't \Nyou capture the Master yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:21:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we can take time to \Nfind out about the drug.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.61,0:21:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of a problem I have,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.78,0:21:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that and that's why \NI need help from you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.81,0:21:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, I just want \Nyou guys to kidnap Caesar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.88,0:21:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.99,0:21:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.92,0:21:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.99,0:21:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Something's flying toward us!\N--It's a big bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.39,0:21:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.82,0:21:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cien Fleurs!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.74,0:21:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.18,0:21:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wham!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.37,0:21:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! He said "Wham"?! Is it a human?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.58,0:22:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.85,0:22:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a nice shortcut!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.80,0:22:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.59,0:22:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will kick your ass and kidnap you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.07,0:22:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, that was supposed to be a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.89,0:22:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.88,0:22:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.77,0:22:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.83,0:22:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That fool! Who said anything \Nabout confronting everyone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.09,0:23:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you, Master?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.18,0:23:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.86,0:23:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A battle unfolds between Smoker's G-5 Navy men and Luffy's crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.13,0:23:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After the violent clash, just when it seems like the research lab will be breached...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.93,0:23:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Caesar's deadly weapon, Smiley, rains down upon person after person...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.21,0:23:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...throwing everyone into fear and chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.39,0:23:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.98,0:23:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"On the Verge of Annihilation! \NA Deadly Monster Comes Flying In!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.36,0:23:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
